replies.author: shree birashpati shidha narayan kumar singh
replies.text: K ko bahula  neta jati pagal bhaisakeyo.

replies.author: Harka khadka
replies.text: Prem ma pagal vaya pachi yastai ho.mukhya mantri ko wief huna bichar hola.
